column5: Sundays outing, The bass gave me the old............. one last shake !!           :
that's musky/pike thumb BUT can pass for bass thumb from tme to time.  PS, ouch.
I got snag arm after I yanked my lure free from a snag! Into another snag
OUCH!!  I think CSIS finally has your prints to compare against the ones found at the crime scene... I knew you would slip up sooner or later!  Craig
that !!!! Its just a flesh wound.
wooo lolz I thought only fish can be snag!... that hurt, i felt that thing too before and I was thinking that how the fish feel... lol that hurt man
All good reasons to wear sunglasses when fishing, always. Even when your night fishing, wear clear glasses. I also add a cape so I can pretend I am a super hero.
was that you I ran into at Wonderland today?      I too wear a cape, of metal to keep me safe!
I've 'ad worse!  Come on back you coward, I'll bite yer legs off!

OUCH X2  I might regret saying this, but I have yet to get a hook into me past the barb. But with as much fishing as a do, it might be inevitable. Be sure that when it happens, OFNers will be the first to know...lol
Yep, merely a flesh wound. Not saying it doesn't suck to get one though.
